	<description>
        ‘Expect Subtle Miracles When Using a Time Bending Machine’ is the most optimistic and ambitious Polygrim record so far. Combining the signature synths and rhythms with acoustic guitars and piano helped us shape the vision of affectionate observation of the world, even in the climate of social insanity. There is a special strength in the subtle beauty that emerges in unpredicted places, the one that often fades away very quickly. We tried to notice this phenomenon and hopefully express in the record.
	</description>
	
